{"tid":2411273,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.18案 余若海反對監警會專家報告呈堂 胡雅文認同不相關 拒接納報告呈堂","createTime":"2021-02-17T08:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:36:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"61aefb9fd3a8a7fe0bbc21dfb0a71da311a0623d","tid":2411273,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:20:30.000Z","msg":"前年反修例運動期間，8月18日民陣發起維園「流⽔式集會」。李柱銘與黎智英等九名泛民主派成員被控當天組織及參與未經批准遊行案，辯方向法庭申請呈交監警會前專家Clifford Stott的專家報告，並申請讓身處英國的Stott以視像設備作供。代表控方的資深大律師余若海表明反對接納專家證供呈堂，直指與本案議題毫無關係，並直指不接受Clifford Stott的專家資格，質疑他在公共安全方面欠缺本地知識，而且Stott曾在網上發表報告嚴厲批評香港警方。法官胡雅文及後作出簡短裁決，認同控方立場，以不相關為由拒絕辯方申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/2QTUR6HBHRE7DDIFZHT66N7APY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F2QTUR6HBHRE7DDIFZHT66N7APY%2F&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN25ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=3f2a8934\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210217%2F2QTUR6HBHRE7DDIFZHT66N7APY%2F&h=b3936324\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210217/2QTUR6HBHRE7DDIFZHT66N7APY/</a>"},{"pid":"6e5387a0080df40ea6f63ebddce06e3b53db8ae6","tid":2411273,"uid":7369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:22:14.000Z","msg":"是鳩旦啦, 都衰撚硬!"},{"pid":"db0784e283dc372379cf593a307f16d589925d88","tid":2411273,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:23:43.000Z","msg":"真係專家就比人人格謀殺，仲叫班毅進教專家上堂"},{"pid":"0b9e54bc23ee7f1ca6d2264bc7d91f9270482147","tid":2411273,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:24:01.000Z","msg":"胡雅文涉司法迫害<br />\n胡雅文師傅馬道立有責任公開解釋"},{"pid":"a0a3595905262c0ee9858a4de54c2fb4585aeadf","tid":2411273,"uid":231480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"胡雅文條奶共肥閪"},{"pid":"a23000adf69f1f1fb868715f2ee69b0742289e2f","tid":2411273,"uid":2